{
  "stem": "3012.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I got off, my parents were waiting for me, and I felt safe with them. 'Safe' in quotation mark.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I decided to go home because I did not expect anything good.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And should anything bad happen, I should be with my family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I would bear an insurmountable guilt today had I not been part of the deportation with my parents.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Had I not been-- had I been sp-- saved from the experience, it would be a horrendous feeling of guilt.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I don't feel survivor guilt because I stayed with them till the very end.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to see my Uncle-- Uncle Bela, who was living in Budapest at the time, and eventually they-- they required-- they required-- or acquired, rather, Christian papers and they were hidden by somebody's chambermaid who was an angel and-- and did extraordinary things for them and for her own employers.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I told him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, well, it's up to you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- I remember he gave me 40 forints just in case.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said goodbye, and I left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And I felt that this-- I made a good decision.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the time I arrived, of course, the invasion was a forgone con-- conclusion.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, it had a foregone conclusion.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had-- the good Hungarians prepared lists of every single Jew in every single town.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the Germans just to take the papers and take it from there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were all apprised of everything, in every single town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Hungarians started to collaborate with the Nazis even before the invasion.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Unless they were warned that something will happ-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't have any way to find this out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I really don't care because I don't care about the Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
